WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:00.410 --> 00:00:06.220
Welcome to the University of Central Lancashire's
new campus in Pyla, Larnaka.

00:00:06.220 --> 00:00:11.509
UCLan has long been recognised as a global
university, and now, we've taken this concept

00:00:11.509 --> 00:00:16.640
to the next level by creating UCLan's first
overseas campus, here, on the Mediterranean

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:18.630
island of Cyprus.

00:00:18.630 --> 00:00:24.241
A blend of high quality academic credentials
and an exceptional student experience, all

00:00:24.241 --> 00:00:29.800
delivered in an award-winning state-of-the-art-campus
setting makes UCLan Cyprus the very best private

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:32.180
university available on the island.

00:00:32.180 --> 00:00:38.239
The key benefits for Cypriot students studying
in Cyprus is access to a British higher education

00:00:38.239 --> 00:00:43.079
experience without the cost and difficulty
of coming to the UK

00:00:43.079 --> 00:00:46.719
For other students in Europe going to Cyprus,
it's a great location offering British higher

00:00:46.719 --> 00:00:49.100
education at an affordable price

00:00:49.100 --> 00:00:53.390
And for British students, it offers them the
opportunity to study at a British university

00:00:53.390 --> 00:00:56.840
with a British curriculum in a great setting.

00:00:56.840 --> 00:01:02.270
Purpose-built to meet EU standards, the UCLan
Cyprus campus is fully equipped with the latest

00:01:02.270 --> 00:01:07.440
state-of-the-art technology - with over 300,000
e-books and e-journals to enhance the teaching

00:01:07.440 --> 00:01:11.620
and learning experience of our students.

00:01:11.620 --> 00:01:16.180
The quality of the campus's technical infrastructure
was recognised by UCLan Cyprus winning the

00:01:16.180 --> 00:01:21.370
2013 InAVation Award for the most technologically
advanced university in Europe, the Middle

00:01:21.370 --> 00:01:24.190
East and Africa.

00:01:24.190 --> 00:01:28.890
The technology brings an impressive new dimension
to the student experience - connecting our

00:01:28.890 --> 00:01:33.080
campuses in Cyprus and the UK for live interactive
lectures and tutorials.

00:01:33.080 --> 00:01:38.830
With our digital resources, we've got the
ability to deliver high-quality material from

00:01:38.830 --> 00:01:41.020
any one of our campuses to any of the other
campuses.

00:01:41.020 --> 00:01:45.360
Now obviously at the moment the main campus
is Preston -- we've got a vast amount of material

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:49.430
we can deliver electronically at any time
of the day or night to one of our campuses

00:01:49.430 --> 00:01:51.090
across the world.

00:01:51.090 --> 00:01:56.280
With a thriving research culture, UCLan Cyprus
is developing its own research centres...

00:01:56.280 --> 00:02:02.640
Through the Centre for Entrepreneurial Development
and Research, we have launched a number of

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:05.770
partnerships with local stakeholders.

00:02:05.770 --> 00:02:13.810
Our students are exposed to practical training
that will allow them to compete in the fiercely

00:02:13.810 --> 00:02:16.700
competitive job market.

00:02:16.700 --> 00:02:21.480
High quality academic standards and a focus
on enhancing the student learning experience

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:25.980
means it's no surprise that so many UCLan
Cyprus students are very satisfied...

00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:31.250
The thing that I like the most about my tutors
is the fact that they clearly know their subject

00:02:31.250 --> 00:02:35.670
very well and they're willing to help us at
any moment with anything, and they're very

00:02:35.670 --> 00:02:36.670
approachable.

00:02:36.670 --> 00:02:41.310
I'm doing exactly what I want, and it's been
an amazing experience so far which is going

00:02:41.310 --> 00:02:44.270
to help me in my future career choice.

00:02:44.270 --> 00:02:52.190
We have a very nice and tight-knit student
community. Our students are committed and

00:02:52.190 --> 00:02:58.210
very engaged in all of their studies and also
extra-curricular activities.

00:02:58.210 --> 00:03:04.670
Student Support helps us to find a job or
inform us about scholarships.

00:03:04.670 --> 00:03:08.910
Whenever we need them, they are available
to help us and support us.

00:03:08.910 --> 00:03:13.730
Only 15 minutes away from the campus, the
city of Larnaka boasts a diverse range of

00:03:13.730 --> 00:03:18.410
shops, bars and restaurants along the beachside
promenade -- a great place to spend your time

00:03:18.410 --> 00:03:22.180
outside the university.

00:03:22.180 --> 00:03:27.040
The accommodation complex is just as impressive
as our campus with a broad range of residential

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:29.310
options and wireless internet throughout.

00:03:29.310 --> 00:03:35.330
It's really nice living here at UCLan Cyprus's
accommodation -- we have spacious apartments,

00:03:35.330 --> 00:03:41.790
nice bedrooms and also a great pool area where
you can meet friends and also relax after

00:03:41.790 --> 00:03:44.310
a hard day at the university

00:03:44.310 --> 00:03:49.069
With high quality degrees accredited in both
the UK and Cyprus and a cutting-edge campus

00:03:49.069 --> 00:03:54.650
that offers real international opportunities,
UCLan Cyprus is your path to a world-class

00:03:54.650 --> 00:03:58.069
British university experience here in Cyprus.

